  <div id="text-content_BEE51E80-2206-0135-3D71-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Self sign-up groups allow users to choose the group they want to be in as part of a group set. You can also limit the number of members who can sign up for each group.</p>
<p><strong>Notes</strong>: </p>
<ul>
<li>You may have to change the group settings later if you want to <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-prevent-students-from-switching-groups-in-self-sign-up/ta-p/689" target="_blank">prevent students from switching sections</a>.</li>
<li>Students are unable to sign up for groups if the <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-manage-Course-Navigation-links/ta-p/1020" target="_blank">People link has been hidden from Course Navigation</a>. </li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>

