      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_BEE70340-2206-0135-3D77-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Create a name for the group set in the <strong>Group Set Name </strong>text field [1]. Click the <strong>Allow self sign-up</strong> checkbox [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
